725223f-a.text:
33rd Avenue, at Prince Street, Flushing, looking north. The houses are on the north side of 33rd Avenue, the former Taylor Avenue, the gas tanks being at 32nd Avenue.
P. L. Sperr  April 8, 1927

727692f-a.text:
Prince Street, west side, between 35th and 33rd Avenues, looking north from near the former, showing most of the houses on the block in a set of two views. The first house in view 2 is the same as the last one in view 1. The first house, to which two wings were added later, was owned by J. Appleby in
187S.
P. L. Sperr  March 12, 1932
NO REPRODUCTIONS  Views 1,2
